        </div>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;">If you have any trouble, try pasting this link in your browser: <a style="color: #28AFB0; word-wrap: break-word;" href="<%= url.resolve(sails.config.custom.baseUrl,'/welcome')+'?token='+encodeURIComponent(token) %>"><%= url.resolve(sails.config.custom.baseUrl,'/welcome')+'?token='+encodeURIComponent(token) %></a></p>
